        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A three-minute energy statement practice from Day 21 of the MONEY program. The statement marks the end of Phase 1: not a new fear to release, but an anchoring of what's been built. Safety with money as a fact, not an aspiration.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
